Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:21.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ringin'  ringin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:19.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君が目の前に突然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:26.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}現れたのは生まれる前から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:29.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}決められていたんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}きっとそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:37.67,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願いや野望や空想が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らない次元でドアを叩いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\shad0\fs12\pos(485,0)}レベル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:49.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}羽ばたく鍵と未来をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}with your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I can hear my heart bell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止められないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}天使が鳴らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「大好き」の合図だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.26,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you hear my heart bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:06.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしたっていうの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:12.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}聞いたことがない胸のベルが鳴る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:15.48,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}それでもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は何にも知らないけれど
Comment: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.87,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我能清楚聽見自己的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.16,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心中的鈴聲響起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一切都從那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.91,0:01:19.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.66,0:01:26.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}出現在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:29.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是早已命中注定的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}沒錯  一定是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:37.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願望  野心還有空想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:43.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}叩響了那通往未知次元的大門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:49.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}天空給了我鑰匙和未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:52.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我能聽見自己的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}已經無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:58.60,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是天使唱響的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那名為「喜歡」的信號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你能聽見我心中的悸動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:06.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:12.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心中響起了從未聽過的鈴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:15.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}然而即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:20.89,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你仍舊是一無所知呢
