Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:09.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去吧  去吧  川口浩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:13.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}去吧  去吧  川口浩
