Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守形學長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點突然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能收留我們一陣子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可保證不了你們的生命安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險  智樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近經常會有熊出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  要是留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會小命不保的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智絕對會到處找內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會讓你住在我家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是來我家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭熊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆被吃掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太無情啦  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在我們是青梅竹馬的份上  這種時候就幫我一把嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能保證不到我的房間裡偷內衣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那櫻井君要來我們家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長會好好款待你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長家好像是那全鎮最大的宅邸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  超名流的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話  見月同學和守形君也一起來如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超名流生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在客氣什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊  守形學長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名流  名流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老夫是美香子的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這五月田根家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡還是驛站的江戶時代起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是掌握著空美鎮的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就說  那個「名流」是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,60)}{\fad(900,0)}{\c&H2226d4&\3c&Hffffff&\fs26}任俠道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,35}{\fad(900,0)}{\c&H2226d4&\3c&Hffffff&\fs22}名流
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也不必這麼害怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不做什麼很過分的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請饒我們一命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快招呼客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺  請用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺  這也請用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們叫學長少爺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為學長和會長是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係很好的緣故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉拉看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小智他剛剛去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這五月田根家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個被稱為  「獄門湯」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只允許本族人使用的浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願智樹這小子別搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？想一起泡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長我倒是不介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢擅自闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井君還意外地有膽色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是趕快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會被殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標正向3點鐘方向逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本族神聖的獄門湯中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闖入了一個毛賊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是美香子的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規矩就是規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獄門湯原本是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月田根家的祖先天女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗淨羽衣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在天女大人離去之後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這浴場曾一度向客人開放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻遭來了天譴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震  饑荒  龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞災難只有割下客人的頭顱才平息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族用「獄門湯」這個名稱祭拜它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是為了保護空美鎮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是美香子的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就盡量給你安樂死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香子  快阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月田根家的規矩是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也無法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  英君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你們還要繼續的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守形的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道想與五月田根家為敵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對主人做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你  你想對我的主人做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚擾各位了  很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  今天就看在這位小姐的份上饒了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來她不是泛泛之輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.14,0:10:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美香子  善後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快到了  大家快起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到無人島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是搞什麼啊
Comment: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是歸五月田根一族所有的小島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請各位盡情放鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  為什麼我們會來到無人島呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為某人把重要的規矩破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果沒法繼續留在家裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是趕各位出去的話又太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想換作去我們家的小島住就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道給各位添麻煩了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不  沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了小智居然能做到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智  你可要好好謝謝人家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙…招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會  真想下海游泳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看無人島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要確保食物充足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？但是  這是會長家的小島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有別墅吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況就是這樣  我們沒時間玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先讓Ikaros和智樹去負責準備食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找能喝的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  Ikaros
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  就在這附近的海裡隨便抓點鯛魚或者金槍魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得  你就大顯身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現椰子蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯  是椰子蟹耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就想嘗一嘗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  差一點就被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄動物  找點植物好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…很顯然是有問題的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐  別這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺  爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…失去意識了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楚原！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點  你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小智你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了  楚原？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒和學長他們在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  我們在逃跑的途中走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是被這聲音追著  拼命逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕啊  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  暫時躲一躲  看看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  等天亮了  我們去找大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夜過後  黎明到來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們前去尋找學長和Ikaros他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  卻完全找不到他們  就這樣過了數日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上  一定會聽到那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智  難道說學長他們已經被吃掉了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  學長他們怎麼會那麼簡單就被幹掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在會長肯定在用無線電求救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓了好多呢  小智
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  拜託你了  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣  過了一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個完全適應了這座島的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楚原也恢復了笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種生活也不錯…什麼的  我開始這麼想的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  我只是想起了學長他們的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小智  我們將來會怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣永遠都沒人來救我們的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時就在這裡愉快地生活下去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在  你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓楚原寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  要是有孩子的話  肯定會更熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  有…孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個…意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楚…楚原…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小智…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快動啊  我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  快動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開楚原！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開  快放開楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開  快放開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金槍魚群實在很難找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去了南半球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智  這個是海帶還有牡蠣什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？難道說這些只不過是纏在Ikaros身上的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在海底行走的時候  被很多東西給纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說  那個聲音是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  要用生命反應雷達探測一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  真是讓人看了場好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是破壞我們一族規矩的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就可以扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓楚原寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  沒有送命就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說我又因為小智而被牽連了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…冷靜點  楚原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底都是小智的錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小智大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房子居然復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  那邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ikaros大姐  你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是五月田根一族的綿薄之禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必收下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於五月田根來說  力量就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸似乎很看好Ikaros
